{"tid":851217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭子誠明寸劉華","createTime":"2018-10-07T03:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T16:27:44.000Z","uid":208675,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff021db5020eda2b661c2c0706b01cfb06148bc1","tid":851217,"uid":208675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"【土地供應】同劉華打對台? 漁護署邀鄭子誠旁白撐保育-<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181007&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58766121 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181007%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58766121%20&d=vZJtk1a3WNlTNIOLyy3BTRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=1b73d5c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181007%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58766121%20&h=23531a52\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181007&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58766121 </a><a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181007&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58766121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181007%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58766121&d=vZJtk1a3WNlTNIOLyy3BTRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d62dee2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181007%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58766121&h=c354c061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181007&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58766121</a><br />\n<br />\n有「民間特首」之稱的影星劉德華繼早前幫警方拍宣傳短片之後，最近又化身「政府代言人」，替團結香港基金錄旁白推廣填海造地方案，力sell東大嶼都會填海方案。<br />\n<br />\n而漁護署就邀請鄭子誠旁白，介紹香港保育的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n在漁護署的影片中，由鄭子誠聲音導航講述香港人的繁囂的都市中，可以讓他們停下來，就是樹木林蔭的郊野和海邊，他形容自己為「生態情人」香港得天獨厚，各個生態環境孕育出豐富物種，片中更有瀕危物種中華白海豚，認為不應該遺忘身邊最寶貴大自然。他在片末提醒大家珍惜大自然：「講咗咁耐，其實我乜嘢陰謀，其實只係想提醒大家，千祈唔好遺忘，香港咁美好嘅大自然」。<br />\n<br />\n而早前劉德華為團結香港基金旁白的影片名為《讓下一代看見》，片長約三分半鐘，提到香港現時面對嘅困局，如「上不到車、租不起樓、上班擠迫、放假更擠迫」，表明「我覺得東大嶼嘅人工島方案睇落係比較可取，可能有人話有排搞，但唔應該因為時間問題而猶豫，相反只要值得做，應該捉緊機會，馬上做。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉德華自1995年開始已經擔任海洋公園的鯨豚保護基金大使，2005年基金擴展為海洋公園保育大使<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靚抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2700cc8db5e6b302140349f12501af01a286fc1","tid":851217,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c23323ae540773740548d357b870f8f06c45447d","tid":851217,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"填海咪會多左海邊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛華都話唔好郁郊野公園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內文與標題不符"},{"pid":"ed05a08deb71fcbc17e7afdb3d35af8406e15b9b","tid":851217,"uid":208675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c23323ae540773740548d357b870f8f06c45447d","tid":851217,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"填海咪會多左海邊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛華都話唔好郁郊野公園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內文與標題不符"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"段片唔剩係指郊野公園<br />\n係成個環境保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f792349f1a0ed72b13aaf48f3f0eab6cf86077d","tid":851217,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ed05a08deb71fcbc17e7afdb3d35af8406e15b9b","tid":851217,"uid":208675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c23323ae540773740548d357b870f8f06c45447d","tid":851217,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"填海咪會多左海邊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛華都話唔好郁郊野公園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內文與標題不符"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"段片唔剩係指郊野公園<br />\n係成個環境保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"